bilingual.source: Unable adj. not able to do something
bilingual.target: 不能的；不会的；无能为力的

bilingual.source: He is an able person, nothing is unable to him.
bilingual.target: 他是一个能人, 对他没有不能的事.

bilingual.source: Nevertheless, even here, he was unable to conceal his fame and prominence.
bilingual.target: 不过， 甚至这里，他是不能的隐蔽他的名声和突起。

bilingual.source: When we are unable to find tranquility within ourselves, it is useless to seek it elsewhere.
bilingual.target: 当我们无法在内心找到宁静时，去别处寻找也是徒劳的。

bilingual.source: Zoo animals can become dependent and be unable to live on their own when returned to the wild.
bilingual.target: 动物园的动物可能会变得依赖，无法在被放归野外时独立生存。

bilingual.source: I am unable to guess his thoughts.
This riddle is truly unable to guess.
He rolls about in bed, unable to sleep.
bilingual.target: 他在床上打滚，无法入睡。

bilingual.source: The target is out of range, unable to hit.
bilingual.target: 目标超出范围，无法击中。

list.abstract: Unable，英文单词，主要用作形容词，作形容词时译为“不会的，不能的；[劳经] 无能力的；不能胜任的”。

yingyinNormal.en: Sir, we were unable to acquire the droid on Jakku.
yingyinNormal.zh: 长官，我们没能在贾库星抓捕到那个机器人。

yingyinNormal.en: As expected, she was unable to complete the puzzle at all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不出所料，她根本无法完成游戏。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Unable to sway the others, he decided to leave the school.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他因为无法说服其他人，因此离开了这所学校。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Therefore, Stan is unable to use self-control. And so he acts out aggressively.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，斯坦没有自制力，所以他总是霸道专横。

yingyinNormal.en: If you are unable to protect yourself in the kingdom, it is I who will be killed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你在这个王国里无法自保，被处死的，将会是我。

yingyinNormal.en: You are no longer a member of the military. You're unable to attend this meeting. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 您不再是军人。你不能参加此审议，我很遗憾。

yingyinNormal.en: Sunlight is often unable to pierce the glue. Even plants struggle to photosynthesis on the worst days.
yingyinNormal.zh: 黑霾压城，阳光往往无法穿透。在最糟糕的时候，即使植物也只能勉强进行光合作用。

yingyinNormal.en: And the whole thing was designed by the same brilliant minds who were unable to capture Rocky and Bullwinkle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而设计这火箭的人可是连飞鼠洛奇和驯鹿布尔温克都抓不到的“聪明”俄国人呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Cactus 1549, if we can get it for you, do you wanna try to land runway 1 -3? We are unable. We may end up in the Hudson.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全美航空1549，如果我们能给你清空跑道，你能尝试降落在跑道13吗？没法办到，我们很可能会迫降哈德逊河。

yingyinNormal.en: But first, I will raise a Sixth Amendment issue. I'm unable to confront my accuser, a non-human entity, to wit, a camera.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但首先，我要提出第六条修正案[美国权利法案]，我无法与控方对峙，因为控方是一台非人类机器，也就是摄像机。

yingyinNormal.en: And finally that you were unable to consummate the marriage. Well, that makes sense since you're gay and addicted to heroin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有你无法履行夫妻间的义务，这也难怪，你是同志，又注射海洛因。

yingyinNormal.en: In the biblical story of the Tower of Babel, all of humanity once spoke a single language until they suddenly split into many groups unable to understand each other.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在圣经故事巴别塔中，所有人类都讲同一种语言，直到他们突然分裂成多个相互之间都听不懂的族群。

yingyinNormal.en: And even if someone slipped a chill pill into their collective drink, you would still be legally unable to work for the next two years. That's for any studio, any network. Television or film.
yingyinNormal.zh: 即使有人往他们公共饮用水里放了镇静药，在法律约束下，你未来两年都无法工作。无论是在哪家工作室、电视台、电视剧或是电影。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what's up? Well, Penny is on her way to perform in a one-night showcase production of rent, which we are unable to attend, because we're going to a symposium on molecular positronium given by Dr. Emil Farman Farmian.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？潘妮正要去一个出租用品展示会进行表演，而我们不能去了，因为我们要去参加由伊米尔·法尔曼法尔米安博士主讲的关于分子正负的研讨会。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes parents get exhausted and frustrated and are <highlight>unable</highlight> to maintain a tolerant and composed style with their kids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时父母会感到疲惫和沮丧，无法对孩子保持宽容和沉稳的风格。

examination_example.sentence: This is why repeated attempts at reform legislation have failed in recent years, leaving the Postal Service <highlight>unable</highlight> to pay its bills except by deferring vital modernization.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是为什么近年来改革立法的多次尝试都失败了，导致邮局无法支付账单，除非重要的现代化进程能够被推迟。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Unable</highlight> to tell whether someone really objects to behavioural ads or whether they are sticking with Microsoft's default, some may press on anyway.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于无法分辨用户是真的反对行为广告，还是他们没有改动微软的默认设置，一些企业可能还是会继续追踪。
